name: Pies
description:
A fragment of feet barely illuminated by the light that goes out, almost in total darkness.
Part of my solo exhibition Tarde, Buenos Aires, 2019.
Acrylic on canvas, 38,5x38,5cm, 2019

Un fragmento de pies apenas iluminados por la luz que se apaga, casi en total oscuridad.
Parte de mi exhibición individual Tarde, Buenos Aires, 2019.
Acrilico sobre tela, 38,5x38,5cm, 2019
